{"word":"θεραπευτέος","slug":"θεραπευτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θεραπευτέος</b></el> <el>(θερᾰπευτέος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:θεραπεύω'><el>θεραπεύω</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one must do service to</i>, <el>τοὺς θεούς</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>one must cultivate</i>, <el>τὴν γῆν</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>one must cure</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}